en world with procedurally-generated content, as well as 9 legend castles to discover and conquer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raid, capture, and upgrade castles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of skills and items to unlock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many side things to do: fishing, finding treasure, dancing, flirting, training weapons and magic...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176090/extras/4003eb1f309a1b3bafcce79109e90c38.poster.avif?t=1767314933\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176090/extras/4003eb1f309a1b3bafcce79109e90c38.webm?t=1767314933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176090/extras/4003eb1f309a1b3bafcce79109e90c38.mp4?t=1767314933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
